{
  "texts": [
    "332 articles were selected for full-text review following title and abstract screening.",
    "267 articles that did not meet the inclusion criteria were excluded, including 104 ongoing or unpublished trial registry entries.",
    "65 RCTs met the inclusion criteria and were included in the final analysis.",
    "Amongst these, four were RCTs of diagnostic test evaluation, where the primary outcome was diagnostic yield (for example, the effect of an assistive AI intervention on a clinician's ability to detect disease) 13, 17, 24, 36.",
    "Whilst these interventional studies did not measure patient outcomes, they were included in this review as the concordance with CONSORT-AI guidelines remains relevant."
  ]
}